cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.CY 

The paper discusses digital forensic evidence acquisition, which involves computer security (cs.CR) and data storage (cs.DS) aspects. The use of a deduplication system also involves database (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE) considerations. Finally, the paper discusses the potential impact on cybercrime investigations (cs.CY).
